		{
			"name": "process-call-event",
			"description": "Entrypoint #2 — process one telephony call event (Flow B, push). Forwards a TelephonyCallEvent JSON to the process-one-event troubleshooter. The requests below cover every distinct path through EventPushSupportingDialerService.processCallEvent (paths A–H, see the entrypoint README.md). Paths A–D work with the checked-in dev/seed-dialers-local.sql (company 9001); paths G and H additionally need processcallevent/seed-appuser-local.sql loaded into honeyfy_dev (the local OPERATIONAL datasource; creates appusers 700501/700601).",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "A — STARTED → 200 skipped (happy path, no seed)",
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Content-Type",
								"value": "application/json"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"companyId\": 9001,\n  \"providerIdentifier\": \"smoke-test-call-1\",\n  \"providerIdentifierType\": \"ENGAGE_DIALER\",\n  \"providerName\": \"gong-connect\",\n  \"callStatus\": { \"type\": \"STARTED\" },\n  \"direction\": \"OUTBOUND\"\n}"
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/telephonysystems/process-call-event?integration-flavor=GONG_CONNECT_API",
							"host": [
								"{{baseUrl}}"
							],
							"path": [
								"telephonysystems",
								"process-call-event"
							],
							"query": [
								{
									"key": "integration-flavor",
									"value": "GONG_CONNECT_API"
								}
							]
						},
						"description": "Path A. callStatus.type=STARTED is not processable (only COMPLETED/FAILED are), so the event is cleanly skipped before any DB/user lookup. Expect 200, body 'Done'. Recommended smoke test — needs no seeded data."
					},
					"response": []
				},
				{
					"name": "B — ERROR: missing callStatus (500)",
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Content-Type",
								"value": "application/json"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"companyId\": 9001,\n  \"providerIdentifier\": \"smoke-test-call-1\",\n  \"providerIdentifierType\": \"ENGAGE_DIALER\",\n  \"providerName\": \"gong-connect\",\n  \"direction\": \"OUTBOUND\"\n}"
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/telephonysystems/process-call-event?integration-flavor=GONG_CONNECT_API",
							"host": [
								"{{baseUrl}}"
							],
							"path": [
								"telephonysystems",
								"process-call-event"
							],
							"query": [
								{
									"key": "integration-flavor",
									"value": "GONG_CONNECT_API"
								}
							]
						},
						"description": "Path B (negative case). callStatus is omitted → isEventOfIrrelevantStatus() NPEs on callStatus().getType(), the outer catch returns unexpectedfailure() (sendToErrorTopic=true), and PushedCallsMetricsReporter rethrows → HTTP 500. This is why callStatus must always be non-null."
					},
					"response": []
				},
				{
					"name": "C — COMPLETED, empty ownerIdentifier → 200 failed (no seed)",
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Content-Type",
								"value": "application/json"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"companyId\": 9001,\n  \"providerIdentifier\": \"smoke-test-call-1\",\n  \"providerIdentifierType\": \"ENGAGE_DIALER\",\n  \"providerName\": \"gong-connect\",\n  \"callStatus\": { \"type\": \"COMPLETED\" },\n  \"ownerIdentifier\": [],\n  \"direction\": \"OUTBOUND\"\n}"
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/telephonysystems/process-call-event?integration-flavor=GONG_CONNECT_API",
							"host": [
								"{{baseUrl}}"
							],
							"path": [
								"telephonysystems",
								"process-call-event"
							],
							"query": [
								{
									"key": "integration-flavor",
									"value": "GONG_CONNECT_API"
								}
							]
						},
						"description": "Path C. COMPLETED is processable, but ownerIdentifier is empty so extractAppUser() returns null → failed() (sendToErrorTopic=false) → HTTP 200, body 'Done'. This is the path the repo's dev/simulate-entrypoints.sh exercises (it sends ownerIdentifier:[]). Reaches processing logic without needing a users-DB appuser."
					},
					"response": []
				},
				{
					"name": "D — COMPLETED, unknown appuser → 200 failed (no seed)",
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Content-Type",
								"value": "application/json"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"companyId\": 9001,\n  \"providerIdentifier\": \"smoke-test-call-1\",\n  \"providerIdentifierType\": \"ENGAGE_DIALER\",\n  \"providerName\": \"gong-connect\",\n  \"callStatus\": { \"type\": \"COMPLETED\" },\n  \"ownerIdentifier\": [ { \"type\": \"APPUSER_ID\", \"value\": \"999999\" } ],\n  \"direction\": \"OUTBOUND\"\n}"
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/telephonysystems/process-call-event?integration-flavor=GONG_CONNECT_API",
							"host": [
								"{{baseUrl}}"
							],
							"path": [
								"telephonysystems",
								"process-call-event"
							],
							"query": [
								{
									"key": "integration-flavor",
									"value": "GONG_CONNECT_API"
								}
							]
						},
						"description": "Path D. COMPLETED with an APPUSER_ID that does not exist in the users DB → extractAppUser() returns null → failed() → HTTP 200, body 'Done'. Same 200-failed outcome as path C but exercises the appUserByIdCache lookup miss."
					},
					"response": []
				},
				{
					"name": "G — COMPLETED, valid user, no integration → 500 [requires users-DB seed]",
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Content-Type",
								"value": "application/json"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"companyId\": 9003,\n  \"providerIdentifier\": \"smoke-test-call-g\",\n  \"providerIdentifierType\": \"ENGAGE_DIALER\",\n  \"providerName\": \"gong-connect\",\n  \"callStatus\": { \"type\": \"COMPLETED\" },\n  \"ownerIdentifier\": [ { \"type\": \"APPUSER_ID\", \"value\": \"700601\" } ],\n  \"direction\": \"OUTBOUND\"\n}"
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/telephonysystems/process-call-event?integration-flavor=GONG_CONNECT_API",
							"host": [
								"{{baseUrl}}"
							],
							"path": [
								"telephonysystems",
								"process-call-event"
							],
							"query": [
								{
									"key": "integration-flavor",
									"value": "GONG_CONNECT_API"
								}
							]
						},
						"description": "Path G [requires seed-appuser-local.sql]. COMPLETED + a valid, active, shouldImportCalls appuser (700601), but company 9003 has NO CONNECTED GONG_CONNECT_API integration (it is AIRCALL/DISCONNECTED in dev/seed-dialers-local.sql). getIntegrationId() throws 'No integration found for company' → unexpectedfailure() → HTTP 500. Load processcallevent/seed-appuser-local.sql into honeyfy_dev first (creates appuser 700601 for company 9003)."
					},
					"response": []
				},
				{
					"name": "H — COMPLETED, valid user + integration → 200 handled (call created) [requires users-DB seed]",
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Content-Type",
								"value": "application/json"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"companyId\": 9001,\n  \"providerIdentifier\": \"smoke-test-call-h\",\n  \"providerIdentifierType\": \"ENGAGE_DIALER\",\n  \"providerName\": \"gong-connect\",\n  \"callStatus\": { \"type\": \"COMPLETED\" },\n  \"recordingStatus\": { \"type\": \"NON_RECORDED\" },\n  \"ownerIdentifier\": [ { \"type\": \"APPUSER_ID\", \"value\": \"700501\" } ],\n  \"startTime\": \"2024-01-01T10:00:00Z\",\n  \"endTime\": \"2024-01-01T10:05:00Z\",\n  \"fromNumber\": \"+15550001001\",\n  \"toNumber\": \"+15550001002\",\n  \"direction\": \"OUTBOUND\"\n}"
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/telephonysystems/process-call-event?integration-flavor=GONG_CONNECT_API",
							"host": [
								"{{baseUrl}}"
							],
							"path": [
								"telephonysystems",
								"process-call-event"
							],
							"query": [
								{
									"key": "integration-flavor",
									"value": "GONG_CONNECT_API"
								}
							]
						},
						"description": "Path H [requires seed-appuser-local.sql] — the true full-ingestion happy path (handled() → HTTP 200, a call/activity is created). Needs ALL of: (1) company 9001 has a CONNECTED GONG_CONNECT_API integration — already true in dev/seed-dialers-local.sql; (2) an active, shouldImportCalls appuser for company 9001 in honeyfy_dev — appuser 700501, created by processcallevent/seed-appuser-local.sql; (3) non-null callStatus AND recordingStatus (recordingStatus is dereferenced unconditionally on this path — a null would 500). recordingStatus=NON_RECORDED keeps it off the recording-download path."
					},
					"response": []
				},
